name: Apple File Conduit "2" (iOS 11+, arm64)「Apple File Conduit“ 2”（iOS 11，arm64）」
author: saurik, Cannathea <csupport@cannathea.com>
description: 「允许arm64设备通过USB进行完整的文件系统访问，尤其是对于使用KPPLess越狱的设备。」Allow full file-system access over USB for arm64 devices, especially for those using a KPPLess jailbreak.
